title: Arbor Snowboards Uncertain Journey Episode 1
description: In a winter of what if's, I wish's and all around WTF's, sometimes you just have to roll the dice and give'er a go. Arbor rider's Ian Sams and Scotty Vine set out on a trek from Salt Lake City to Aspen and then on to Denver just trying to get involved and make some snowboarding happen in a wildly uncertain season. Along the way they drop in on a SLC urban mission, a Nike Chosen event, the Bonezone, Brighton, the X Games, Snowmass and SIA among all parts in-between and at various times they meet up with teammates, Sean Black, Brandon Hammid, Blake Axelson, Sammy Spiteri and Nick Visconti. Arbor Snowboards presents an Uncertain Journey Episode 1 of 2.
